<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   P&amp;G, Pressured by Boycott, to Market
   Coffee Blend Without Salvadoran Beans
   ----
   By Gabriella Stern
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
11/15/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B5
</SO>
<CO>
   MO PEP PG Z.NES
</CO>
